    "title": "Web Application Threat Model",
    "owner": "Abhilash Tarigopula",
    "description": "This threat model describes the security architecture of a web application system. \nThe system includes a human user accessing the web application through HTTPS. \nThe web application communicates with backend services that process requests \nand interact with a SQL database and file storage system. \n\nThe model identifies potential security threats using the STRIDE methodology \nand proposes mitigations to protect system components and data flows.",
